Title : Luberizi
Text : '''Luberizi''' is a town in the [[South Kivu|province of South Kivu]] of the [[Democratic Republic of Congo]]. At an elevation of 957 metres, it has a local population of about 25,462.<ref name="Luberizi, Congo">{{cite web | url=http://www.fallingrain.com/world/CG/12/Luberizi.html | title=Luberizi, Congo | accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref> It sits astride the N5 road where it crosses the Luberizi River, nearly midway between [[Uvira]] to the south and [[Bukavu]] to the north.

